85 			JLT 	$LOOP 		  HAS BEEN REACHED 	 
90 	$EXIT 		STX 	&amp;amp;RECLTH		SAVE RECORD LENGTH 	 
95 			MEND 	

				(a) 	

			RDBUFF 	Fl,BUFFER,LENGTH 


