&lt;h2 id=&#34;recursive-macro-expansion&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#recursive-macro-expansion&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Recursive Macro Expansion&lt;/h2&gt;
